title: Studio Apartment Home! Gym On Site! W/D On Site
posting_body: ['WELCOME HOME TO THE CORNELIUS', 'If you are looking for urban living, look no further.', 'The Cornelius Apartment Homes is located in the Belltown neighborhood in the heart of downtown Seattle.', 'With a stunning renovation completed in 2010, this 1925 building has maintained its vintage charm with a modern twist.', 'The homes are spacious with large walk-in closets and some of the best views of the Puget Sound, the Space Needle, Lake Union, and the lights of the Emerald City.', 'The Cornelius provides a professional on-site management and maintenance team.', 'We will listen to your needs, return calls promptly and address any concerns immediately.', "You're not just a resident, you're a neighbor when you rent with us.", 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'More unit details at:', '<URL>', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 424-431 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Dishwasher', '- Refrigerator', '- Carpeting', '- Extra Storage', '- View', 'Community Amenities', '- Elevator', '- Bike Racks', '- Pet Wash', '- On-Site Management', '- Historic Building', '- Fitness Center', '- Laundry Facilities', '- Package Receiving', '- On-Site Maintenance', '- Recreation Room', '- Free Weights', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets - allowed', 'Cats - 2 allowed', 'Dogs - 2 allowed', 'Office Hours', 'Monday - Friday: 9am to 6pm', 'Saturday: 10am to 5pm', 'The Cornelius', '306 Blanchard Street, Seattle, WA, 98121', 'CKu19feuO']
